<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 17 of the Act Governing Food Sanitation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Foods to be eaten raw means such foods to be served after preparing treatments like washing and peeling.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Products shall have their original pleasant flavor or color. No putridity, discoloration, off odor and flavor, contamination, moulds, foreign matter or parasite shall be found.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
